# MOBILE::CELL_CAM_ACTIVATE_SELFIE_MODE

## Summary
Turn on/off the selfie (reverse angle) mode of the cell phone camera. Only visible when the cell phone camera is active

## Parameters
* **BOOL** shouldActivate
